Left of centre Nana . Enjoys photography,birds, food, road trips , Roses, the veggie garden and knitting.
My avatar is a small bird ,a fantail, perched on a branch watching the photographer intently. My banner image was taken by my photography buddy.
I am standing on a beach with my back to the camera. I have a 150 to 600 lens trained on a bird which is out of shot. The Pacific Ocean is the softly focused backdrop. It is me in my happy place
